      "writtenOn": "2018-11-02T23:34:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t agree we need the client-side configs design ready before migrating. It\u0027s orthogonal, we can easily rename VMs later to match any desired conclusions from the client-side configs design.",
      "parentUuid": "7273c9ea_00386bae",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 67,
        "startChar": 0,
