        "id": 1141499
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-02T23:49:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agree it\u0027s orthogonal.\nYes, we can migrate just to service-side configs, and then we can migrate again to client-side configs.\nHowever, this would mean mucking with configs twice, and in either case it requires involvement from our clients.\nSo, why pay this cost twice?",
      "parentUuid": "18d7f38d_34158f6a",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 67,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 69,
        "endChar": 20
      },
      "revId": "ab1a0d60846d64beacbccec0b03a648270a50881",
